{Speech 2}{}{Hi! My name is T-Ray, this is my workshop. I buy, sell, repair and modify cars here. I can help, if you have money, of course. Also I can make a copy of any key for 1000 coins.}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{What units do you have in stock?}
{Speech 2 Answer 10}{}{I'd like to sell my car.}
{Speech 2 Answer 30}{}{What else can you offer to me?}
{Speech 2 Answer 40}{}{Make a copy of this key.}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{Sorry, I'll visit you later.}
{Speech 3}{}{I can offer You: Hummer for @lex hummer@, Buggy for @lex buggy@, Scout for @lex scout@, Highwayman for @lex highwayman@.}
{Speech 3 Answer 3}{}{I'll buy Hummer.}
{Speech 3 Answer 3*}{}{I'll buy Buggy.}
{Speech 3 Answer 3**}{}{I'll buy Scout.}
{Speech 3 Answer 3***}{}{I'll buy Highwayman.}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{No, maybe next time.}
