{Speech 7 Answer Exit}{}{That's it! Bye.}
{Speech 8}{}{Here's the key, car is waiting for you in the garage. If you'd like to repair or modify it, you're welcome.}
{Speech 8 Answer Exit}{}{That's it. Bye.}
